erience/tooling in the Foundry portal. For example, “Grounding with Bing Search” and “Bing Custom Search” have classic versions, with guidance increasingly pointing to newer “Web Search tool”/tool catalog docs depending on the API you’re using. 【5:2†source】【5:3†source】\n\n## When you’d use it\nUse Foundry Agent Service when you want an agent that:\n- integrates with enterprise data/tools,\n- can take reliable actions (not just chat),\n- and needs deploy/operate features (safety, scaling patterns, observability hooks) rather than bespoke infrastructure. 【5:0†source】\n\nIf you tell me your scenario (e.g., IT helpdesk agent, invoice processing, internal knowledge assistant, customer support triage), I can map the typical Foundry Agent Service components/tools you’d pick.","annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/overview","start_index":374,"end_index":386,"title":"What is Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/overview","start_index":607,"end_index":619,"title":"What is Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/overview","start_index":732,"end_index":744,"title":"What is Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry-classic/agents/how-to/tools-classic/overview","start_index":984,"end_index":996,"title":"What are tools in Foundry Agent Service? (classic)"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/overview","start_index":1206,"end_index":1218,"title":"What is Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry-classic/agents/how-to/tools-classic/overview","start_index":1527,"end_index":1539,"title":"What are tools in Foundry Agent Service? (classic)"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry-classic/agents/how-to/tools-classic/bing-grounding","start_index":1892,"end_index":1904,"title":"How to use Grounding with Bing Search in Foundry Agent Service (classic ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry-classic/agents/how-to/tools-classic/bing-custom-search","start_index":1904,"end_index":1916,"title":"How to use Custom Bing Search with Foundry Agent Service (classic ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/overview","start_index":2200,"end_index":2212,"title":"What is Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"}],"logprobs":[]}],"status":"completed"},"output_index":2,"sequence_number":508}

